title: Alawar Games - 10 Days Under The Sea - Hidden Object - Requested
description:
10 Days Under The Sea

Do you believe in ghosts? If not, you&#039;d better start, 
because in 10 Days Under the Sea, you&#039;ll be playing as one! 
When Carrie opens a compass belonging to her father, 
an old man appears, turns her into a phantom and says 
he&#039;ll restore her to the land of the living if she finds 
all of the treasures he lost in ten days. If you don&#039;t help 
Carrie meet her deadline, she&#039;ll be trapped forever 
in the spirit world!
Hunt for hidden objects at ten locations, use hints to beat 
the clock and activate artifacts that can help you locate the 
hardest to find items. For a change of pace, go fishing for 
photos of exotic ocean life. Challenging and relaxing in equal 
measure, 10 Days Under the Sea is so enchanting, you&#039;ll never
 want to come up for air!
